                    <span>If Strunk and White had gone to business school, this is the book they would have written. It's an antidote to the interminable memo, the pointless presentation, and the endless e-mail.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Keep this one on your desk - it works!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
